name: Tech Titans
title: Leading in Medium and High-Tech Exports
description: In 2022, the Philippines excelled with 80.02% of its manufactured exports being medium and high-tech, showcasing its prowess in advanced manufacturing and technology sectors.

name: Eco-Friendly Footprint
title: Minimal Methane Emissions from Industry
description: The Philippines reported a mere 0.0001 Mt CO2e of methane emissions from industrial processes in 2023, reflecting its commitment to sustainable industrial practices.

name: Health Hurdles
title: High Women's HIV Prevalence
description: In 2022, 6.63% of women aged 15+ in the Philippines were living with HIV, highlighting a significant public health challenge that needs urgent attention.

name: Family Planning Success
title: Low Wanted Fertility Rate
description: The wanted fertility rate in the Philippines was 1.5 births per woman in 2022, indicating effective family planning and reproductive health policies.
